*** Keywords ***

Random postal code
    [Documentation]  Generates a BC postal code at random (likely to not exist)
    ${first_number} =  Generate Random String  1  [NUMBERS]
    ${second_number} =  Generate Random String  1  [NUMBERS]
    ${third_number} =   Generate Random String  1  [NUMBERS]
    ${second_letter} =  Generate Random String  1  [UPPER]
    ${third_letter} =   Generate Random String  1  [UPPER]
    [Return]  V${first_number}${second_letter}${second_number}${third_letter}${third_number}

Random licence plate
    [Documentation]  Generates a BC postal code at random (likely to not exist)
    ${first_set} =  Generate Random String  3   [NUMBERS]
    ${second_set} =  Generate Random String  3  [UPPER]
    [Return]  ${first_set}${second_set}

Random VIN
    [Documentation]  Generates a VIN-like 17-digit alphanumeric number at random (probably not be valid).
    ...              For details of what an actual VIN looks like, See:
    ...               https://www.autozone.com/diy/trustworthy-advice/what-does-each-digit-in-a-vin-mean#h-world-manufacturer-identifier
    ${vin_like_number} =  Generate Random String  17   [UPPER][NUMBERS]
    [Return]  ${vin_like_number}